    </label>
    <label class="radio sub">
      <input type="radio" name="hosting" value="20_minus">
      <em>Tiny budget</em> - I want to spend as little money as possible and accept the limitations it puts me under.
    </label>
    <label class="radio sub">
      <input type="radio" name="hosting" value="20_plus">
      <em>Flexible budget</em> - I am willing to spend $20(USD)/month or more to get the most flexibility.
    </label>


  <label class="radio">
    <input type="radio" name="have_hosting" value="yes">
