  </label>
    <label class="radio sub">
      <input type="radio" name="hosting" value="shared">
      <em>shared hosting plan</em>
    </label>
    <label class="radio sub">
      <input type="radio" name="hosting" value="server">
      <em>my own server, or VPS</em>
    </label>

  <p>How comfortable are you with Perl?</p>
  <label class="radio">
    <input type="radio" name="perl" value="0">
